description: The game is over but the hard play has just begun, as newbie Aaron London and Dacotah Red engage in a little overtime once they get home from the gym. Dacotah may have been high scorer in the game, but in the bedroom, Aaron is the big winner, as he fucks Dacotah all over the bedroom. Dacotah shows that his ball handling isn't confined to the court, and that he's more than ready for any kind of hard wood situation. And when Aaron finally takes his shot, it ends in a perfect splash, just the kind of play Dacotah had drawn up in his fantasy. Enjoy!
title: Ballin' Buds
